package_description="This package includes all experiments and fun by Kugi.\n
List of changes and features:\n
- One-handed mode: Swipe to the left/right at the bottom empty bar\n
- Floating mode: In one-handed mode, drag the handle located at the top left\n
- Word select: In cursor mover mode, double-tap while the cursor is in the middle of a word without selecting any text\n
- Commit words when using buttons like go to start/end of line\n
- Increased word ribbon height\n
- Custom height in portrait and landscape (For 16:9 devices)\n
- Other minor changes that I can't remember XD"
